Simple Music Synthesizer (SiMSynth)
A simple synthesizer GUI program written in Rust.

It must have a possibility to play multiple sounds, as well as them at once without the degradation of quality.
It should have an out-of-the-box expirience, but also a configuration for additional customization (UI, keybinds, sounds, if they are only preset).
It may have unbound notes, keyboard driven expirience, a way to save and read the music back, a way to export to a widespread musical format (MP3 or other).

No AI was used in the project. For new for me tasks some code may be coming from online documentation, StackOverflow or some learning cites.

